Elsa and Olaf were busy enjoying the wonderful sports activity skating and suddenly they met with an accident and fell down. Olaf was shattered into several pieces and the lovely dress of your cute princess Elsa also got dirty. They both look much tensed and no one is there except you to help them out. Would you come forward to show your precious helping hands? Join Elsas Laundry Time game and be prepared to take care one of the funniest and challenging jobs you have ever accepted in the virtual world!

Your primary objective in this brand new dressing game for girls is to put Olaf back together and then start checking out the wardrobe of the princess Elsa to help her change her dirty clothes. The wardrobe is full of lovely and neat & clean dress. Give her a beautiful white gown and combine with a blue, pink or a silver color pair of shoes or choose a purple gown and combine it with a dark purple color sandal in this html5 princess dress up game!

Your creativity and fashion abilities will surely guide you to help both to sort out this difficult time. It will take only a few clicks to help your princess get clean outfits in this fun simulation game. Separate the white colored outfits from the colored fabrics and send them to undergo a proper cleaning! Do not forget to leave them in the sun for sometimes to dry properly! Complete the last step by helping princess iron their clothes! Have fun on atmegame.com, without download games!
